Email Node
================================================================================

Summary
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

THe Email Node module lets the admin to send a node to a list of users seleceted through checkboxes 


Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Email Node Term module requires the Taxonomy (core) and the UsersTax module .
The Drupal Mailer should be configured 


Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Copy the Emailnode folder to sites/all/modules or to a site-specific
   modules folder.
2. Go to Administer > Site building > Modules and enable the Email Node     module.


Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Associate users with the taxonomy using the Userstax Module .
2. Go to Administer -> Content Management -> Content -> Select the node you wish to email . Then click on Send Email .
3. Select the users through the checkboxes and modify the subject and the body if needed .
4. Click on Send Mail . Tada ! Your mail is sent 



